			<title>KURMA RUPA DASA - Cow protection &quot;Care for Cows&quot;</title>
			<link>http://www.audarya-award.org/page/dharma-presentation/8-kurma-rupa-dasa-cow-protection-qcare-for-cowsq</link>
			<guid>http://www.audarya-award.org/page/dharma-presentation/8-kurma-rupa-dasa-cow-protection-qcare-for-cowsq</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;">Care for Cows is a very special cow´s protection program at Vrindavan  leading by Kurma Rupa Dasa. They are providing food, shelter and care  for the abandoned cows in Krishna’s holy land.</p>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3841 720x480.jpg" alt="" width="400" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>

<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div style="text-align: center;">Care for Cows Inc. maintains abandoned  cows, bulls, retired oxen, and orphaned calves. They are international  volunteers who offer their talents and resources to tend to the  neglected cows living in Krishna's holy land Vrindavana.</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3897 720x480.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">They provide stray cows hay, flour, fresh grass, medical attention and a  place where they can recuperate from injuries. At present we host a  herd of four hundred.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc chandi.jpg" alt="" height="128" /> <img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc hamsa.jpg" alt="" height="128" /> <img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc kunti.jpg" alt="" height="128" /> <img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc lala.jpg" alt="" height="128" /> <img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc madri.jpg" alt="" height="128" />&nbsp;<img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/cc nakula.jpg" alt="" height="128" /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<br />There are approximately three to four hundred abandoned cows in Vrindavan requiring accommodation.</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center;">Unless they are protected they are destined to subsist on refuse and  become plagued by various debilitating and often terminal diseases or  suffer injury from careless motorists.</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">However, the most immediate danger is that they become abducted for  slaughter by cattle rustlers who are active in this area today.</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center;">HOW YOU CAN HELP?</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">There are many different programs at Care for Cows Goshala:</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center;">-Life Adoption Program</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-General Donation</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Feed Cows for a Day</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Feed Cows a feast on that Special Day</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Feed Cows a feast on your birthday, anniversary, when a child is born, etc.</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Maintain the Resident of Your Choice</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Bull Scholarships</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Sponsor our Monthly Medical Expenses</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Build an Oxcart</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">-Build a new Cowshed</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3886 720x480.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">World Vaishnava Association´s secretary, Sripad Priyananada Bon Maharaj gave the Audarya Award to Sriman Kurma Rupa Dasa</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3823 720x480.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3849 720x480.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Also Sripad Bhaktivedanta Sadhu Maharaj came to the event</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.audarya-award.org/page/images/stories/photos/cow_protection/img_3826 720x480.jpg" alt="" /></p>
